/* Useful for removing trailing characters of a defined type. 
   Example remove all trailing . in     Lorem Ipsum...
   
   Step 1. Select the column you want to apply the trim to and perform a normal transform > trim. 
   Step 2. Go to the Advanced Editor and find the newly added trim step. 
   Step 3. Change the code Text.Trim  to  each Text.TrimEnd(_,".")
   
           Change the . do any wanted character.
*/

each Text.TrimEnd(_,".")


